#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/barcode.rst:2
msgid "条形码检测（Barcode）"
msgstr "Barcode Inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/barcode.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/barcode.rst:6
msgid "识别一维条码 / 二维码，并将读出的序列号用于与历史检测记录关联（如 PCB 唯一序列号），支持批次追溯与按子板归档。"
msgstr ""
"Reads 1D and 2D barcodes and links the decoded serial number to inspection "
"history (for example, as a PCB unique serial number). Supports batch "
"traceability and per-sub-board archiving."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/barcode.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/barcode.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the tool's "
"parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/barcode.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/barcode.rst
msgid "条码工具参数"
msgstr "Barcode tool parameters"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/barcode.rst:18
msgid "框选包含条码的区域即可；系统在检测时自动读取并记录条码内容，无需额外阈值参数。"
msgstr ""
"Just drag-select the region containing the barcode; during inspection the "
"system reads and records the barcode value automatically. No threshold "
"parameters are required."
